msgstr "Talk_Think"

msgctxt "84_Tanimura"
msgid "Excuse me. Did you happen to see some men leading a woman\\r\n"\n"away against her will?"
msgstr "Disculpe. ¿Vio usted si unos hombres se llevaron a una mujer a\\r\n"\n"la fuerza, como si la estuvieran secuestrando?"

msgctxt "96_Businesswoman"
msgid "Yes! As a matter of fact, I did! They took her away\\r\n"\n"in a car!"
msgstr "¡Sí, sí los vi! ¡Se la llevaron en un auto a toda\\r\n"\n"velocidad!"

msgctxt "108_Tanimura"
msgid "Did they say anything about where they were headed?"
msgstr "¿Dijeron algo sobre a dónde iban?"

msgctxt "120_Businesswoman"
msgid "Well... I was so shocked and it all happened so fast...\\r\n"\n"But... I did hear them shouting something."
msgstr "Pues... Me agarró tan de sorpresa y todo pasó tan rápido...\\r\n"\n"Pero... sí escuché que gritaban algo."

msgctxt "132_Tanimura"
msgid "Do you remember what it was they were they shouting?\\r\n"\n"Any bit of information would really help me out."
msgstr "¿Recuerda qué era lo que gritaban? Cualquier detalle me\\r\n"\n"ayudaría un montón."

msgctxt "144_Businesswoman"
msgid "Right, of course. Let me think... Oh yeah, I remember\\r\n"\n"it was something about the ocean!"
msgstr "Ah, sí, claro. Déjame pensar... Ah, sí, ya me acuerdo,\\r\n"\n"¡Era algo sobre el océano!"

msgctxt "156_Businesswoman"
msgid "Yes, it was definitely something about the\\r\n"\n"ocean, like a place down on the coast."
msgstr "Sí, sin duda era algo relacionado con el océano,\\r\n"\n"como un lugar allá en la costa."

msgctxt "168_Tanimura"
msgid "I see. Thanks for your help."
msgstr "Entendido, Muchas gracias."

msgctxt "180_Tanimura"
msgid "(The ocean... So they really must've gone down to the docks.)"
msgstr "(El océano... Así que seguro que fueron a los muelles)."

